Module: vioser.sys — virtio-console (single-port virtio-serial) driver.
Surfaces \Device\VirtioCon0 with IRP_MJ_READ and IRP_MJ_WRITE; reads
return bytes the host pushed into the chardev, writes surface on the
host's chardev sink. Links against the shared virtio.lib (NTOS/VIRTIO).

QEMU device: virtio-serial-pci, vendor 0x1AF4 device 0x1003 (legacy).

!ENDIF

MAJORCOMP=ntos
MINORCOMP=dd

TARGETNAME=vioser
TARGETPATH=$(BASEDIR)\public\sdk\lib
TARGETTYPE=DRIVER

INCLUDES=..\..\inc;..\..\virtio\inc

TARGETLIBS=$(BASEDIR)\public\sdk\lib\*\virtio.lib

SOURCES=vioser.c \
        vioser.rc
